{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>ViuTV年度音樂盛事《CHILL CLUB推介榜 年度推介25/26》今晚（5月3日）盛大舉行。許志安驚喜現身擔任表演嘉賓，先與MIRROR成員AK（江𤒹生）合唱《翻</p><p>ViuTV年度音樂盛事《CHILL CLUB推介榜 年度推介25/26》今晚（5月3日）盛大舉行。許志安驚喜現身擔任表演嘉賓，先與MIRROR成員AK（江𤒹生）合唱《翻騰》。許志安着閃片外套和戴帽，型爆跳唱，型仔程度不輸AK。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127713117166374912169534.jpeg/jjJ_7l09N7VDexi8UsVAnvxZSB08-xUy9Xor1Nx6K9Q\" alt=\"許志安驚喜現身做表演嘉賓。（陳順禎 攝）\"><figcaption>許志安驚喜現身做表演嘉賓。（陳順禎 攝）</figcaption></figure><p>許志安驚喜與AK Alton型爆跳唱</p><p>其後許志安再與AK、Alton（王智德）跳唱《Rebound》，三人組合十分新鮮，期間許志安模仿美國流行天王Michael Jackson表演，擺出MJ的招牌扶帽姿勢，58歲的他狀態Fit爆，令人眼前一亮！</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127713928806666240197204.jpeg/fdP5ULGIHgG2n4eleh1118b70UkwmRmdB9dHtT7XR7U\" alt=\"同AK同台。（陳順禎 攝）\"><figcaption>同AK同台。（陳順禎 攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127713925543366656954321.jpeg/2k027pIkwnqRJLZZWskKumh-E5Iua-KcXUVwGWRFcBk\" alt=\"型。（陳順禎 攝）\"><figcaption>型。（陳順禎 攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127713922473005056168357.jpeg/MiWNtXJWvSekm589Jo_EqcnsgqvqkDu-66ot8dKqLfE\" alt=\"58歲狀態好Fit。（陳順禎 攝）\"><figcaption>58歲狀態好Fit。（陳順禎 攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127713919591387136798651.jpeg/i56fE2Lmkrr_UgpiH2E6rTbnNQLMKmJfNf38Uwz9_FM\" alt=\"勁。（陳順禎 攝）\"><figcaption>勁。（陳順禎 攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127713916219035648562708.jpeg/glYVkMhgCq3spWNp8FkWsPFt_J5MgnzcE31lNCp9ZTQ\" alt=\"AK型。（陳順禎 攝）\"><figcaption>AK型。（陳順禎 攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127713895327207424501893.jpeg/uqyDmOnx0425cvV6PKY938ovbd7yYP0dIuVYXBvlWFw\" alt=\"AK同Alton。（陳順禎 攝）\"><figcaption>AK同Alton。（陳順禎 攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-03T15:33:15.125383+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":423,"images":7,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}